WEBVTT

00:02.045 --> 00:03.829
Previously on "Mr. Mercedes"...

00:03.873 --> 00:05.353
Ollie Ollie Oxen Free.

00:05.396 --> 00:07.311
Come on out, Brady.

00:07.355 --> 00:09.009
I did not kill a dog!

00:09.052 --> 00:10.488
Al, they've got you
on tape!

00:10.532 --> 00:11.663
Babineau: Now the patient's
reacting very strongly

00:11.707 --> 00:13.143
to the visual stimuli.

00:13.187 --> 00:14.840
That's a short,
concrete sign off progress.

00:14.884 --> 00:16.625
Yet the patient
is still nonverbal?

00:16.668 --> 00:17.930
Clearly, you're
missing something.

00:17.974 --> 00:18.931
What's your objective here?

00:18.975 --> 00:20.063
We want
Brady Hartsfield gone.

00:20.107 --> 00:21.760
Shipped to Crestmore.

00:21.804 --> 00:23.066
What did you say to him
in the hospital?

00:23.110 --> 00:24.981
I asked him why
he spared my life.

00:25.025 --> 00:27.505
So, Ireland?
With Donna.

00:27.549 --> 00:29.116
Yep, Ireland.

00:29.159 --> 00:30.204
Thought any more
about school?

00:30.247 --> 00:31.074
You going back?

00:31.118 --> 00:31.727
What if I want
this life?

00:31.770 --> 00:33.076
That's fine.

00:33.120 --> 00:35.035
Be a part of it
with a Harvard degree.

00:35.078 --> 00:36.732
Felix,
give me my passport.

00:36.775 --> 00:37.994
Tell me the truth.

00:38.038 --> 00:39.909
Did Vitalta demand
that you go to China?

00:39.952 --> 00:41.128
No.

00:41.171 --> 00:42.607
So much for being
in this together.

00:42.651 --> 00:43.869
You haven't cut your hair
in three weeks?

00:43.913 --> 00:45.088
Now, remember --
not too short, huh?

00:45.132 --> 00:45.697
Little trim.

00:45.741 --> 00:47.786
Around the ear.

00:47.830 --> 00:49.136
-Razor.
-[ Groans ]

00:49.179 --> 00:50.920
-Ohh!

00:50.963 --> 00:52.008
I'm not Al.

00:52.052 --> 00:53.096
I'm Brady Hartsfield.

00:53.140 --> 00:54.402
For a spot of tea?

00:54.445 --> 00:56.012
-Can't I --
-Ida?

00:56.056 --> 00:57.753
-Elliot, this is Bill.
-Hi, Bill.

00:57.796 --> 00:58.971
How are you doing?

00:59.015 --> 01:00.451
[ Dog barks ]Aah!

