47:02.863 --> 47:04.343
Mr. Pettimore --
He just came in --

47:04.386 --> 47:06.562
Pettimore was misinformed.
He knows that.

47:06.606 --> 47:08.869
You can call him if you like,
but on your time.

47:08.913 --> 47:10.653
On my time, all of these
machines need to be

47:10.697 --> 47:13.482
hooked back up -- now.

47:13.526 --> 47:14.396
You know,
it's not your hospital.

47:14.440 --> 47:16.659
No. It's my ward.

